{"tid":29103,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人試過養寵物前先斬後奏？","createTime":"2016-12-08T10:56:21.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-27T11:10:31.000Z","uid":39924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c9619a835fefc6b309c0d349343ee747b8db87c9","tid":29103,"uid":39924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T10:56:21.000Z","msg":"係咁既，一直想養隻貓，但係屋企人反對，話覺得貓好臭。果陣細個冇意見，宜家了黎做野，有經濟能力，想領養隻翻屋企養。但又驚屋企人反對，好矛盾呀。有冇人有相關經驗呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b12bbb88517a71615ba326ab692dde13abb5408","tid":29103,"uid":39924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T10:56:48.000Z","msg":"出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9c390fc8ac217d1f739b1405dc10620a7794cad","tid":29103,"uid":21871,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T10:57:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係咁既，一直想養隻貓，但係屋企人反對，話覺得貓好臭。果陣細個冇意見，宜家了黎做野，有經濟能力，想領養隻翻屋企養。但又驚屋企人反對，好矛盾呀。有冇人有相關經驗呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我老豆不嬲反對養狗<br />\n宜家佢好鍾意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />日日同佢玩"},{"pid":"6c04981d2e2eb5ed3b34a05727652b5b26128320","tid":29103,"uid":6472,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T11:00:35.000Z","msg":"有呀，我屋企兩隻主人都係先斬後奏"},{"pid":"3d6344518cc5a3ee3e25087208c391bd6a776ba0","tid":29103,"uid":39924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T11:39:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>係咁既，一直想養隻貓，但係屋企人反對，話覺得貓好臭。果陣細個冇意見，宜家了黎做野，有經濟能力，想領養隻翻屋企養。但又驚屋企人反對，好矛盾呀。有冇人有相關經驗呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我老豆不嬲反對養狗<br />\n宜家佢好鍾意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />日日同佢玩</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n直接拎佢翻去屋企人點講呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"606637d4f7520a83c703c79d1f627b137fd24e62","tid":29103,"uid":39924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T11:40:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有呀，我屋企兩隻主人都係先斬後奏</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n但我屋企淨係係我好細個養過小動物<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dba50fbaecd37786423fb0dd76f63a3a46e74596","tid":29103,"uid":1408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T11:40:35.000Z","msg":"話個朋友擺住先<br />\n擺擺下就長擺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a82d082a73ef153f8cd9351c60495c66349be46","tid":29103,"uid":33749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T11:45:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>話個朋友擺住先<br />\n擺擺下就長擺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我識人都係咁"},{"pid":"4d27b2ed7400573e2a8b918357677acdda58c44b","tid":29103,"uid":15658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T11:45:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>話個朋友擺住先<br />\n擺擺下就長擺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我識人都係咁</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nSame here<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13526effdd831dfc1e2ee95466a5952b90277c52","tid":29103,"uid":54324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T11:48:51.000Z","msg":"唔知算唔算先斬，媽媽知我studio有養隻貓仔，有時見到我張wallpaper都會讚可愛。佢一開頭係超反對養，覺得又臭又煩，不過我個日照拎左返屋企佢返到黎先話佢知，佢而家無野做就走入黎撩佢玩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但當然如果無溝通清楚結果最後有啲極端既屋企人會偷偷送走佢地 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 所以自己衡量下"},{"pid":"0a26986024f8822a239d065ea197531fcbf0856a","tid":29103,"uid":4807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T11:49:01.000Z","msg":"拎左番去先 最後屋企人通常都會變埋貓奴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d06c6fa07183d3e25d70dfea4708a0341ed9859","tid":29103,"uid":21034,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T11:49:16.000Z","msg":"同問<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好耐以前已經想先斬隻貓返屋企<br />\n但係家父超級潔癖 每隔兩個鐘就執一次腳毛頭髮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a2233b88c97e6f57e03ddfba41c4b8dfad64c9d","tid":29103,"uid":39924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T11:59:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>話個朋友擺住先<br />\n擺擺下就長擺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我識人都係咁</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nSame here<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n但我同我屋企人都冇養貓狗經驗，話擺住先應該佢地唔會信<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47a45720d7023c56d8ca15ace0720bf8669bc223","tid":29103,"uid":39924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T12:00:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔知算唔算先斬，媽媽知我studio有養隻貓仔，有時見到我張wallpaper都會讚可愛。佢一開頭係超反對養，覺得又臭又煩，不過我個日照拎左返屋企佢返到黎先話佢知，佢而家無野做就走入黎撩佢玩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但當然如果無溝通清楚結果最後有啲極端既屋企人會偷偷送走佢地 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 所以自己衡量下</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都好驚佢地會偷偷送走佢 不過考慮到佢地早出晚歸一個星期得一日假 我諗我只要係果一日𥄫實應該冇事？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a25ad0ce1ce612e650cedfe4a51315d66a6f793","tid":29103,"uid":39924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T12:02:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>同問<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好耐以前已經想先斬隻貓返屋企<br />\n但係家父超級潔癖 每隔兩個鐘就執一次腳毛頭髮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我屋企人就冇潔癖 但就怕佢地唔中意到發癲dup出街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f78bfa12a336af540b413303747a3c94f72029e","tid":29103,"uid":1408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T12:02:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>話個朋友擺住先<br />\n擺擺下就長擺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我識人都係咁</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nSame here<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n但我同我屋企人都冇養貓狗經驗，話擺住先應該佢地唔會信<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n話朋友俾埋貓紗<br />\n又淨係信得過我<br />\n到時執生啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ecf49e8fd4dd1baa672b29d605eb4a79af5d96ec","tid":29103,"uid":32727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T12:04:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>同問<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好耐以前已經想先斬隻貓返屋企<br />\n但係家父超級潔癖 每隔兩個鐘就執一次腳毛頭髮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n做咩斬貓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d947348c5ad5656b8b400265aacb656d5e7c3e2","tid":29103,"uid":12180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T12:05:31.000Z","msg":"我屋企兩隻都係先斬後奏，第一隻果陣瘋狂鬧我，家嘈屋閉左幾星期，之後就開始日日討好隻貓，後來我帶多隻返黎而家日日乖仔前乖仔後<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n當然你要幫隻貓諗定後著，如果真係強烈反對到隻貓有危險你都可以搵人安置返佢地"},{"pid":"314d7931907c98dc2492494a2326d17f19995e9b","tid":29103,"uid":42246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T12:05:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係咁既，一直想養隻貓，但係屋企人反對，話覺得貓好臭。果陣細個冇意見，宜家了黎做野，有經濟能力，想領養隻翻屋企養。但又驚屋企人反對，好矛盾呀。有冇人有相關經驗呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n到時你屋企人扔佢出街 <br />\n唔係你屋企人錯 係你責任<br />\n屋企人表明左自己立場<br />\n你都唔尊重 到時你屋企人都唔會尊重你<br />\n你一返工返學 漁農處見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申：我隻貓係屋企人先斬後奏帶返來同你情況一樣<br />\n我就冇意見 但我呀媽就嬲到出煙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3409427093d79f7d9add4fde1671ac327197c63f","tid":29103,"uid":26329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T12:06:14.000Z","msg":"養貓 得屋企變埋貓奴 搞掂"},{"pid":"5360d7ea30a10b944d84232a4a0d3336259050df","tid":29103,"uid":7125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T12:08:46.000Z","msg":"我係隻寵物先斬後奏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 條鹽蛇未問過我就做左我全家寵物"},{"pid":"e5449dcc49b500d8e088ff02ff0ad16e392f1c19","tid":29103,"uid":26998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T12:25:59.000Z","msg":"我係有一期同關係唔好，搬左出去住<br />\n後來無事好返，我媽係咁叫我搬返去<br />\n我同佢講搬返黎ok，但我帶埋隻貓<br />\n唔ok就唔搬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咁佢想我搬返黎，咪硬食囉<br />\n<br />\n初初都有唔鍾意，因為隻貓好撚曳<br />\n後尾養多兩隻添<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"754e1d6d3759b9859f8dd052b052f1eabbbf0a29","tid":29103,"uid":12712,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T13:39:56.000Z","msg":"我養刺蝟先斬後奏，有日我媽見到有個箱，問我用黎做咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果養小動物既都可以接受，但你養貓曠最好同家人討論下，畢竟體形較大仲會四圍走<br />\n你仲要留意一下家人既脾氣或者有冇對動物敏感，最後問下自已係咪冷靜諗過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a918c85addf6a44cdca2ed2f5d128505028c653f","tid":29103,"uid":57771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T13:42:25.000Z","msg":"無<br />\n但買哂成屋貓月具先<br />\n放好哂位<br />\n俾定心理準備屋企<br />\n最後連屋企人都肯陪我去睇領養"},{"pid":"243e8e42ceec213f76af6945e6fc07c479525221","tid":29103,"uid":43595,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T13:50:30.000Z","msg":"我就係成功既例子 當年15.6歲 個陣呀媽好憎狗 我偷偷地帶左隻狗返去之後無理佢 我呀媽就慢慢變到好錫我隻狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"133592ac16f730dfae2b45daa8c4a0854b35b9fa","tid":29103,"uid":1967,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T13:56:11.000Z","msg":"我家姐班朋友送左隻狗比佢做生日禮物<br />\n送上黎個刻全屋呆晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f1186abb5a82f0aff7023f7014d0013eb41def6","tid":29103,"uid":30793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T13:58:32.000Z","msg":"老豆本身唔比養狗<br />\n跟住呀媽無通知聲就買左<br />\n三姊弟拎埋隻狗上老豆公司<br />\n本來老豆都唔中意隻狗<br />\n但而家反而最錫佢 電話wallpaper都係隻狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b8b77e43683b1cccc57040a93247344a4f59d07","tid":29103,"uid":14413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T14:02:04.000Z","msg":"我係失敗例子<br />\n<br />\n上 個月拎咗佢返黎<br />\n<br />\n屋企人唔鍾意<br />\n<br />\n好啦放係房習慣下先<br />\n<br />\n一直好地地 逐漸放佢出廳<br />\n<br />\n但我媽間中發神經 我都無野<br />\n<br />\n直至有日我老豆失驚無神用拖鞋飛佢<br />\n<br />\n我同細佬就同老豆老母嘈<br />\n<br />\n咁就困佢係房<br />\n<br />\n早幾星期去個旅行<br />\n<br />\n期間佢唔知係咪掛住我<br />\n<br />\n日日係上格床痾屎 老豆母仲反對 <br />\n<br />\n我返黎佢就唔敢痾 但係我返工佢又痾...<br />\n<br />\n依家長困係房先 呢幾日放假佢先收斂啲去返貓砂"},{"pid":"41cea5bf549531d91c49b60589b1e255db7c5a89","tid":29103,"uid":21871,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T15:59:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>係咁既，一直想養隻貓，但係屋企人反對，話覺得貓好臭。果陣細個冇意見，宜家了黎做野，有經濟能力，想領養隻翻屋企養。但又驚屋企人反對，好矛盾呀。有冇人有相關經驗呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我老豆不嬲反對養狗<br />\n宜家佢好鍾意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />日日同佢玩</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n直接拎佢翻去屋企人點講呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n直接話我比錢買左隻狗，隔一個月拎左番去<br />\n利申支持領養"},{"pid":"328cd3292ee8f7be06dc9188f1dc2d9733f3ae91","tid":29103,"uid":25463,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T16:11:47.000Z","msg":"第一隻狗先斬後奏，屋企人好反對<br />\n因為隻狗皮膚病成身腐屍味一郁d味就飄埋黎<br />\n我教佢十八般武藝又醫返好佢<br />\n而家隻狗比我更得寵<br />\n佢地間唔中會接寄養狗過黎連問都唔問我<br />\n仲同我講隻狗好慘架，唔收留佢無人理佢架啦<br />\n有隻寄養狗直頭係我屋企寄養到百年歸老<br />\n火化果日我老豆喊到收唔到聲<br />\n之後執左2隻貓b, 果兩隻野頑皮到無法無天<br />\n成日襯人行過申手除人條褲<br />\n我老豆咩都由佢地玩<br />\n呀媽就日日引導隻貓叫佢做呀媽<br />\n我完全無地位"},{"pid":"cdf0c3c23d312210c59d5589506229fae7f7092d","tid":29103,"uid":39924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T06:35:25.000Z","msg":"睇哂咁多人既事我決定暗示下睇下呀媽咩反應先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n俾佢鬧我就預左 如果佢地真係好反感就唯有等出黎自已住再養喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0920a93dd73d547c1e767761778731ed39b37e5","tid":29103,"uid":30487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T06:37:20.000Z","msg":"次次見有咩魚鐘意就買返屋企養<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7e461583dc5a14e6e48eec2950bf6954d4637e6","tid":29103,"uid":40348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T06:43:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係咁既，一直想養隻貓，但係屋企人反對，話覺得貓好臭。果陣細個冇意見，宜家了黎做野，有經濟能力，想領養隻翻屋企養。但又驚屋企人反對，好矛盾呀。有冇人有相關經驗呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n利申 真人真事<br />\nFd 隻貓生左b<br />\n<br />\n首先換左老母部ipad wallpaper 換左隻貓相<br />\n<br />\n老母：你拎佢返黎就紅燒貓仔肉<br />\n<br />\n第二日問fd 借個籠 同運貓器<br />\n<br />\n老母：你拎返黎做乜<br />\n我無理佢<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n拎完 放左入籠<br />\n<br />\n老豆：你書都未撚讀掂 養乜撚野貓<br />\n<br />\n我：得啦<br />\n<br />\n之後比我發現老豆烏低身望貓望左10分鐘<br />\n<br />\n當時兩個月我有份產屎<br />\n<br />\n2個月打後老豆自動搶晒黎做<br />\n<br />\n老母開頭唔理佢<br />\n<br />\n之後就日日問 貓貓餓唔餓阿 <br />\n<br />\n煮雞雞/蝦蝦你食好無呀<br />\n<br />\n我=<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4fc9bb303b7014160062771b4d726108100968d","tid":29103,"uid":50298,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T06:51:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>係咁既，一直想養隻貓，但係屋企人反對，話覺得貓好臭。果陣細個冇意見，宜家了黎做野，有經濟能力，想領養隻翻屋企養。但又驚屋企人反對，好矛盾呀。有冇人有相關經驗呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n利申 真人真事<br />\nFd 隻貓生左b<br />\n<br />\n首先換左老母部ipad wallpaper 換左隻貓相<br />\n<br />\n老母：你拎佢返黎就紅燒貓仔肉<br />\n<br />\n第二日問fd 借個籠 同運貓器<br />\n<br />\n老母：你拎返黎做乜<br />\n我無理佢<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n拎完 放左入籠<br />\n<br />\n老豆：你書都未撚讀掂 養乜撚野貓<br />\n<br />\n我：得啦<br />\n<br />\n之後比我發現老豆烏低身望貓望左10分鐘<br />\n<br />\n當時兩個月我有份產屎<br />\n<br />\n2個月打後老豆自動搶晒黎做<br />\n<br />\n老母開頭唔理佢<br />\n<br />\n之後就日日問 貓貓餓唔餓阿 <br />\n<br />\n煮雞雞/蝦蝦你食好無呀<br />\n<br />\n我=<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af79ece6446b9986599bc8cd39bae8645604240d","tid":29103,"uid":4158,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T13:54:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我係失敗例子<br />\n<br />\n上 個月拎咗佢返黎<br />\n<br />\n屋企人唔鍾意<br />\n<br />\n好啦放係房習慣下先<br />\n<br />\n一直好地地 逐漸放佢出廳<br />\n<br />\n但我媽間中發神經 我都無野<br />\n<br />\n直至有日我老豆失驚無神用拖鞋飛佢<br />\n<br />\n我同細佬就同老豆老母嘈<br />\n<br />\n咁就困佢係房<br />\n<br />\n早幾星期去個旅行<br />\n<br />\n期間佢唔知係咪掛住我<br />\n<br />\n日日係上格床痾屎 老豆母仲反對 <br />\n<br />\n我返黎佢就唔敢痾 但係我返工佢又痾...<br />\n<br />\n依家長困係房先 呢幾日放假佢先收斂啲去返貓砂</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n各位先斬寵物之前諗清楚老豆老母接唔接受到先好"},{"pid":"feee64c1a1dd80e0a727b6bb067b5bc20ffa63fc","tid":29103,"uid":16783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T15:04:45.000Z","msg":"失敗既話隻寵物會好慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4695629778a0d50acf55cd016c9e65c8653a2c45","tid":29103,"uid":22505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T16:20:14.000Z","msg":"有，我隻狗仔就係<br />\n同老豆老母講想養一定會反對<br />\n咁岩我老母去左旅行老豆就去左返工<br />\n之後個日約定左個朋友佢陪我去買<br />\n個日係隻狗同埋其他咩一次過買哂<br />\n都老豆老母返黎見到隻狗冇乜大反感<br />\n只係話｢我唔會幫佢清潔架｣就算<br />\ne加老豆老母都好鐘意佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n由其是係老母佢成日買好多正野比隻狗食<br />\n仲要係全部都唔平<br />\n<br />\n不過我d屋企人本身都唔會憎狗<br />\n如果樓主屋企人係憎貓又有鼻敏感既話<br />\n我都係勸你唔好養費事又多一單遺棄寵物<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89bcab716e369cdb8ed3725af897d1f0a6005263","tid":29103,"uid":27793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T05:13:11.000Z","msg":"我係<br />\n得阿媽阿妹鍾意動物<br />\n阿爸麻麻<br />\n算係3:1<br />\n之後我夾硬帶返去養 bb貓黎 適應得好快又爹人<br />\n<br />\n後來而家個個都鍾意隻貓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n阿爸最鍾意 鍾意到抱著訓覺"},{"pid":"19d736ecdd763a102771415d8da6b9328d93d8f3","tid":29103,"uid":21654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T06:19:37.000Z","msg":"點解個個case屋企人係初初唔鐘意<br />\n到最後變左係最錫寵物嗰個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e642f467048878933deb0523645e5aa06c3f8404","tid":29103,"uid":4326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T06:28:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點解個個case屋企人係初初唔鐘意<br />\n到最後變左係最錫寵物嗰個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nExact7ly<br />\n<br />\n老母叫隻貓做仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n夜晚訓教又會自動跳去老母張床<br />\n<br />\n對佢仲好過我<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0fc9e2e5fb6b7a34f7f38a774f95f709cc0b9814","tid":29103,"uid":15987,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T06:36:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>同問<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好耐以前已經想先斬隻貓返屋企<br />\n但係家父超級潔癖 每隔兩個鐘就執一次腳毛頭髮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n做咩斬貓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a74e08e4a94e40389ac83ffb2e7923549b9db7cc","tid":29103,"uid":95,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T07:09:34.000Z","msg":"尊重下屋企人啦。你想養就得，你屋企人覺得臭就唔得。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9487a4097bc209d2e146a9a783c12385add9f4fd","tid":29103,"uid":22147,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T10:10:54.000Z","msg":"兔仔倉鼠先敢 因係唔會周圍走 貓狗果d真係唔敢 同埋要裝野一定比人屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f69e2288027ca37986ce5cf884bc7f4d3209042f","tid":29103,"uid":39924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T10:13:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>尊重下屋企人啦。你想養就得，你屋企人覺得臭就唔得。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n冇唔尊重 我咪講左話佢好反感我就出黎自己住再養<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01dd2e8624f330c6f5f0f0027e34c22484118a7b","tid":29103,"uid":25212,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T11:47:16.000Z","msg":"其實屋企人反對，唔係驚要照顧佢，係唔想當有感情後個種離別既傷感<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0935aac145e3b19e28e1b6630bf50d72f89b91bb","tid":29103,"uid":49359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T12:23:36.000Z","msg":"上年有隻貓仔成日同佢玩<br />\n之後俾人攞左去養<br />\n我成日諗起佢<br />\n早知當時攞返屋企<br />\n我阿爸成日都係街同野貓玩<br />\n佢話自己養就麻煩"},{"pid":"0b149d8a60e61a6dcbc201e8e83d3645baa6761b","tid":29103,"uid":63304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T16:37:15.000Z","msg":"路過<br />\n<br />\n貓貓臭唔臭同佢飲食好有關<br />\n我朋友養1隻陣貓除大味過我養2隻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nBTW 我係搬出黎先養貓嘅<br />\n阿爸阿媽有哦 不過管我唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6fccd07c68ef66ef832fffe7913b5e5d7bfc3f4","tid":29103,"uid":64092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T16:45:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我家姐班朋友送左隻狗比佢做生日禮物<br />\n送上黎個刻全屋呆晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁大整蠱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"420a94d5cd793e91d7ffc6e1d01bbe30bbffd51c","tid":29103,"uid":64092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T16:56:11.000Z","msg":"我算半先斬後奏,<br />\n係有通知而唔算同意嘅情況下帶隻老鼠返屋企,<br />\n係有尾嗰隻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n開頭老豆老母都勁抗拒,<br />\n最後鍚到佢燶<br />\n<br />\n建議扮已經預備好晒帶返屋企差佢up頭,<br />\n睇下有咩反應,<br />\n事前比佢鬧餐死好過第時隻貓死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"235a5fcde49cc43d98b50a8bb3246e326b1af2a9","tid":29103,"uid":43607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T16:57:19.000Z","msg":"最後唔比你養咁點"}]}